  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div xml:id="NA391-kiḷavi">
            <p type="edition">1. itu pirivuṇarttapaṭṭu āṟṟāḷāyt (EV: ākiya) talamakaḷait tōḻi vaṟpuṟuttatu (EN, ER, ET, EV: vaṟpuṟuttiyatu). 2. varaivuṇarttiyatūumām. (missing in ET)</p>
            <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">1. This is how the confidante encouraged HER who was unable to bear it when being informed of the separation. 2. It is also how the marriage was announced.</p>
            </div>
      <div xml:id="NA391">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            āḻaṉ maṭantai yaḻuṅkuvar celavē</l>
<l>            pulippoṟi yaṉṉa puḷḷiyam potumpiṟ</l>
<l>            paṉippavar mēynta māyiru maruppiṉ</l>
<l>            malartalaik kārā ṉakaṟṟiya taṇṇaṭai</l>
<l>            yoṇṭoṭi makaḷi riḻaiyaṇik kūṭṭum</l>
<l>            poṉpaṭu koṇkāṉa naṉṉa ṉaṉṉāṭ</l>
<l>            ṭēḻiṟ kuṉṟam peṟiṉum poruḷvayiṉ</l>
<l>            yārō pirikiṟ pavarē kuvaḷai</l>
<l>            nīrvār nikarmala raṉṉaniṉ</l>
<l>            pēramar maḻaikkaṇ ṭeṇpaṉi koḷavē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>            Don’t be overwhelmed, girl, he will refrain from going.</l>
<l rend="indent">            Even if he were to get the Ēḻil hill</l>
<l rend="indent2">            in Naṉṉaṉ’s good land in the gold-yielding Koṇkāṉam mountains,</l>
<l rend="indent3">            where bright-bangled women compound [their] jewel decoration</l>
<l rend="indent4">             in the arable tract that broadens onto flower-headed buffalo cows</l>
<l rend="indent4">            with big dark horns that grazed on the dewy creepers</l>
<l rend="indent4">            in the grove dotted<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">puḷḷiyam potumpiṉ</term>: here the question arises whether <term xml:lang="ta">puḷḷiyam</term> is simply an adjective formation or whether it rather refers, as to be expected in this position, to a particular species of plant.</note> as if with tiger-spots,</l>
<l>        who will be able to separate [from you] for wealth,</l>
<l rend="indent2">            so that your big beautiful eyes take clear dew,</l>
<l rend="indent3">            as water-dripping rival blossoms of the blue waterlily?</l>
<lg type="alternate" sameAs="10b">
  <l>while he takes in the clear dew of your big beautiful eyes...</l>
</lg>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
